Package: mc3logit
Type: Package
Title: Matched Case-Control Conditional Logit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("George G", "Vega Yon", role = "aut",
           comment = "Original author; see LICENSE"),
    person("Sima", "Najafzadeh", email = "u1418987@umail.utah.edu", role = "cre")
    )
Description: The "mc3logit" package implements permutation-based inference for
  conditional logistic regression models. Permutation-based methods for matched
  case-control logit were notably used by Ridgeway (2016). The package includes
  tools for fitting permutation-based conditional logit models
  (clogit_perm()), simulating matched case-control event data (sim_events(),
  sim_events2()), and computing dynamic exposure covariates (exposure_dyn()).
